text: Suomen huippumalli haussa, Cycle 6 is the sixth season of the Suomen huippumalli haussa series that began to air on 15 March 2017. The judging panel was revamped with Maryam Razavi as the host, and Juri Silvennoinen and Marica Rosengård as co-judges. Additionally, male hopefuls were allowed to apply introducing a co-ed cycle. The winner of the competition was 20 year old Jerry Koivisto from Hämeenkyrö. He won a modeling contract with Paparazzi models, a Cosmopolitan cover and a flight to New York City for castings.
